dashboardItems.text: An effective BEmONC facility should have provided all 14 basic signal functions within the past 3 months. A BEmONC-1 facility provided all but one; and a BEmONC-2 facility provided all but 2
*Please note* : A health facility should have all five infrastructure elements to effectively provide CEmONC.
An effective CEmONC facility should have provided all 14 basic signal functions within the past 3 months. A CEmONC-1 facility provided all but one; and a CEmONC-2 facility provided all but 2
*Please note* : A health facility should have all five infrastructure elements to effectively provide IEmONC.
An effective IEmONC facility should have provided all 14 basic signal functions within the past 3 months. A IEmONC-1 facility provided all but one; and a IEmONC-2 facility provided all but 2
